net.dean.jraw.managers

Class ThingCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.dean.jraw.managers.ThingCache

  • public class ThingCache
extends java.lang.Object
    Maintains a map of Thing names and Things inside of WeakReferences. ThingManager is a singleton and can be accessed anywhere.
